1
00:01:03,650 --> 00:01:05,900
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:09,860
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:17,400
Zhao.

4
00:01:20,230 --> 00:01:23,430
Miss Jiang, the empress dowager
requests your presence.

5
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,590
Your Majesty.

6
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:37,509
There's no need to be so forceful.

7
00:01:37,509 --> 00:01:39,039
You are my elder.

8
00:01:39,150 --> 00:01:41,229
How could I refuse your invitation?

9
00:01:43,509 --> 00:01:46,640
You're just like your mother.

10
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,590
Claiming indifference with your words,

11
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:51,920
yet all of you are desperate
to worm your way into the palace.

12
00:01:52,150 --> 00:01:54,200
My mother always respected you.

13
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:55,759
She's gone now.

14
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:58,840
Please stop slandering her like this.

15
00:01:59,289 --> 00:02:01,400
How dare you talk back to me!

16
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,000
You want to be empress?

17
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,590
I could make that happen.

18
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:11,800
But how dare you trick Nianzhao
with a fake imperial seal!

19
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,960
I've never seen that imperial seal before.

20
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:16,400
If Prince Nianzhao
hadn't opened that book box,

21
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,870
no one would have known that Xie Jiuzhao

22
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:20,120
had hidden a fake
imperial seal in the palace.

23
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,280
The bargaining chip
between Prince Nianzhao and me

24
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:25,010
has always been
only what I have in my possession.

25
00:02:25,380 --> 00:02:27,900
[Imperial Study]

26
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,280
Guards!

27
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,040
Your Majesty.

28
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:45,150
Seal off the palace.

29
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,310
Keep all those ministers under watch.

30
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,079
Yes, Your Majesty.

31
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,560
Your Majesty.

32
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,030
Prince Nianzhao sent word.

33
00:02:52,190 --> 00:02:53,470
There's a secret passage in the study.

34
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:55,240
Xie Jiuzhao has returned.

35
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:56,560
Please...

36
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:59,120
Please move to the main hall for safety.

37
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,750
The hastily made imperial robe

38
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,680
just doesn't fit right.

39
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,590
You came alone.

40
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:06,910
Aren't you afraid of dying?

41
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,310
Where is Jiang Li?

42
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,150
Rebellious son Xie Jiuzhao.

43
00:04:17,829 --> 00:04:19,360
Just as I thought.

44
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:21,310
Just like your father,

45
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,160
you can't let go of this woman.

46
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,360
Guards!

47
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:27,950
Arrest the traitor Xie Jiuzhao!

48
00:04:28,430 --> 00:04:29,360
Guards!

49
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,630
You all...

50
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:43,800
Your Majesty,

51
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,750
all the rebels in the palace
have surrendered.

52
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:47,920
The ministers have
all been taken care of as well.

53
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,950
Very good.

54
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,720
Jiuzhao, you truly have impressive skills,

55
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,190
silently

56
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,920
bringing so many troops into the palace.

57
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:59,830
Why don't you surrender immediately?

58
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:04,830
No matter what,

59
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:07,070
you cannot change

60
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:09,920
the fact that you're not of royal blood.

61
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,430
Is that so?

62
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:17,310
You two, mother and son,
are plotting to usurp power.

63
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:19,640
The court officials are waiting outside.

64
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,810
It's time to show them

65
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:24,240
the letter from the late Emperor.

66
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,240
Whether one is of royal blood

67
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,640
will be clear at a glance.

68
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,750
He is your own brother!

69
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:31,720
Xie Jiuzhao.

70
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,390
You're nothing but a demon.

71
00:05:34,409 --> 00:05:35,409
That's right.

72
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,830
I am a demon.

73
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,560
So I won't show any mercy.

74
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,159
Jiuzhao.

75
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:53,070
Whether you have hatred or grudges,

76
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:55,159
it's all my fault.

77
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:57,310
If you can't let go,

78
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,560
then I'll die. I'll die.

79
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,800
-Can you let Nianzhao go?
-Mother!

80
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:07,480
No, no.

81
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,160
I haven't lost yet.

82
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:11,480
Ling's Army is right outside.

83
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,120
With just one command from me...

84
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,120
You think I pretended to be captured

85
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,500
and stalled you for days for what reason?

86
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,490
I have made my decision.

87
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,560
If you come again,

88
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:26,730
our master-servant relationship will end!

89
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,070
Your Majesty!

90
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:29,630
Guards!

91
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,480
Take the commander away
to treat his wounds.

92
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,720
After he recovers,

93
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:37,130
exile him to Suzhou
and conscript him into the army!

94
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:41,360
I don't want to see you again.

95
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:50,159
The empress dowager is trying to lure
the tiger away from the mountain.

96
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,950
Let's turn her plan against her.

97
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:53,170
Take the token of command
and the imperial seal

98
00:06:53,170 --> 00:06:54,480
to Suzhou to mobilize troops.

99
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,880
There's no time to waste.

100
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,700
The Suzhou army
is already outside the city.

101
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,070
Messages calling for
loyal forces to rescue the emperor

102
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,430
have been sent throughout the realm.

103
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:07,090
You have no chance of winning!

104
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,750
Fine.

105
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:16,390
Then I'll fight to the death
for my last chance!

106
00:07:16,430 --> 00:07:17,480
Nianzhao!

107
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,240
No!

108
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:29,040
You want the palace to run with blood,

109
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:31,000
your people to slaughter each other.

110
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:33,070
Is this how you rule as emperor?

111
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:36,000
Winners become kings;
losers become outlaws.

112
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,920
Jiuzhao,

113
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,800
just end it quickly.

114
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:17,680
Nianzhao,

115
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:21,800
if you're done with this drama,

116
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:25,870
come walk with me in the imperial garden.

117
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,680
Do you like these flowers?

118
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:10,860
[Young Xie Nianzhao]

119
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:12,870
Mother used to say

120
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:14,120
flowers are useless,

121
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:16,870
just trinkets for women to fuss over.

122
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:19,240
Stay here. Don't follow me.

123
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,870
Jiuzhao, is this for me?

124
00:09:30,390 --> 00:09:32,120
I don't think flowers are useless.

125
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,390
They flourish so beautifully

126
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:35,450
and leave a fragrance in one's heart.

127
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,670
But don't let Mother find out.

128
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,790
W-What are you doing?

129
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,750
I love you the most, Jiuzhao.

130
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,840
I'm going to read. Don't disturb me.

131
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,320
I understand, Jiuzhao.

132
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,800
When you were little,

133
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,260
you always liked to follow me around.

134
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:04,360
Though I seemed indifferent,

135
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,910
deep down,

136
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,770
I was actually happy
to have you as my brother.

137
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,150
What's the use of saying this now?

138
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,910
It's all too late.

139
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,150
I'm nothing but a bastard.

140
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,510
For someone like me,

141
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,720
the only end is death.

142
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,270
Nianzhao.

143
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:35,510
I will pass the imperial seal to you.

144
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,240
From now on,

145
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,500
you are the Emperor of the Zhao State.

146
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,550
What did you say?

147
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,050
No matter who your birth father is,

148
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,640
I acknowledge you as my brother.

149
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:52,120
Heaven favors no one, only virtue matters.

150
00:10:52,550 --> 00:10:53,630
For me,

151
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,050
compared to the throne,

152
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:58,200
I'd rather spend
the rest of my life with the one I love.

153
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,550
The palace is not for me.

154
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:04,120
You have a kind and earnest nature.

155
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:06,200
I believe your succession

156
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:09,120
is what the people truly want.

157
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,600
Thank you, Jiuzhao.

158
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,000
Nianzhao.

159
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:27,470
The path ahead is difficult.

160
00:11:27,510 --> 00:11:29,670
I will help you from the shadows.

161
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:31,680
And keep watch over you.

162
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,660
I hope you will rule in my stead

163
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:38,510
and bring peace
and prosperity to the people.

164
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,670
Li!

165
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:08,750
Li.
